Definition: any plant of the genus Lithops native to Africa having solitary yellow or white flowers and thick leaves that resemble stones
Synonyms: living_stone, stoneface, stone-face, stone_plant, stone_life_face, flowering_stone, succulent, genus_Lithops, m, any, plant, of, the, genus, Lithops, native, to, Africa, having, solitary, yellow, or, white, flowers, and, thick, leaves, that, resemble, stones
Category: noun.plant
